overview: Come one, come all to witness Maverick, the Mystifying Oracle! Err…Oracle in training. Waking up from one helluva morning after, no-nonsense Lindsay realizes that her mother has ordered a psychic for her birthday. Enter all-nonsense Maverick, Madame Lulu’s newest protégé who gives Lindsay a birthday surprise she’ll never forget…
title: Maverick the Mystifying Oracle
